### CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing) preflight 
### tests. They verify that your API allows requests 
### from web clients running on different origins.
### Should return 200 OK with appropriate CORS headers 
### if configured correctly.

### Preflight Request - Timers
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/timers
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: x-api-code

